	@{" Change  " Link CK_Change }	@{" Display          " Link CK_Display  }	@{" Reply       " Link CK_Reply  }	@{" Next      " Link CK_Move     }	@{" Shell         " Link CK_Shell  }
	@{" Reload  " Link CK_Reread }	@{" Goto... next     " Link CK_Move     }	@{" Group reply " Link CK_Group  }	@{" Previous  " Link CK_Move     }	@{" Pipe          " Link CK_Pipe   }
	@{" Resync  " Link CK_Resync }	@{"         previous " Link CK_Move     }	@{" Extend. g.r." Link CK_ExtGrp }	@{" Redisplay " Link CK_Redisplay}	@{" Palette       " Link CK_Palette}
	@{" Edit    " Link CK_Edit   }	@{"         first    " Link CK_GotoFirst}	@{" Forward     " Link CK_Forward}		@{" Alias         " Link Aliases   }
	@{" Iconify " Link CK_Iconify}	@{"         number   " Link CK_GotoNum  }	@{" Bounce      " Link CK_Bounce }		@{" Options       " Link CK_Opts   }
	@{" About   " Link CK_Version}	@{"         pattern  " Link CK_Search   }	@{" Send new    " Link CK_Mail   }		@{" List commands " Link CK_Cmds   }
	@{" Quit    " Link CK_Quit   }	@{" Tag/untag        " Link CK_Tag      }	@{" Metamail    " Link CK_Mime   }		@{" Extra Program " Link CK_Prog   }
	@{" Exit    " Link CK_Exit   }	@{" Untag all        " Link CK_Untag    }
		@{" Save             " Link CK_Save   }
		@{" Save with header " Link CK_Write  }
		@{" Print            " Link CK_Print  }
		@{" Delete           " Link CK_Delete }
		@{" Undelete         " Link CK_Delete }
		@{" Mark unread      " Link CK_Unread }
		@{" Decrypt          " Link CK_Decrypt}
@{CLEARTABS}
@{BODY}

@{myheadline "Shifted keys"}

Use  the  shifted  command keys for reply, forward, bounce and group reply to
get  the  whole  message  (with header) included in your message.  By default
only  the  message  body  (text)  is  included.   Use  shift for exit/quit to
exit/quit quickly (without any confirmations).

@EndNode

